qDefinition:
SELECT 
        "3aLv3STLST".GLT_AB                    AS "GLT_AB",
        "3aLv3STLST".GLT_BIS                   AS "GLT_BIS",
        "3aLv3STLST".ERF_AM                    AS "ERF_AM",
        TF2TG0.ID_NR                           AS "ID_NR",
        "3aLv3STLST".TC0TD0_POL_NR             AS "TC0TD0_POL_NR",
        "3aLv3STLST".TC0TD0_ZUST_C             AS "TC0TD0_ZUST_C",
        "3aLv3STLST".TC0TD0_LF_NR              AS "TC0TD0_LF_NR",
        TF2TG0.TC0T18_ID_NR                    AS "TF2TG0.TC0T18_ID_NR",
        TF2TG0.TC0TC0_LF_NR                    AS "TF2TG0.TC0TC0_LF_NR",
        TF2TG0.T20T20_ID_NR                    AS "T20T20_ID_NR",
        TF2TG0.ABH_ROL_C                       AS "ABH_ROL_C",
        TF2TG0.FKT_C                           AS "FKT_C",
        TF2TG0.FKT_NR                          AS "FKT_NR",
        TF2TG0.LF_NR                           AS "LF_NR",
        TF2TG1.T19T19_ID_NR                    AS "T19T19_ID_NR",
        TF2TG1.UNIV_WERT                       AS "UNIV_WERT",
        "3aLv3STLST"."2aLV2STLST.TC0T18_ID_NR" AS "2aLV2STLST.TC0T18_ID_NR",
        "3aLv3STLST"."2aLV2STLST.TC0TC0_LF_NR" AS "2aLV2STLST.TC0TC0_LF_NR"
    FROM 
       ( SELECT
        "2aLV2STLST"."TF2HD0.GLT_AB"  AS "GLT_AB",
        "2aLV2STLST"."TF2HD0.GLT_BIS" AS "GLT_BIS",
        "2aLV2STLST"."TF2HD0.ERF_AM"  AS "ERF_AM",
        TF2HC0.TC0TD0_POL_NR          AS "TC0TD0_POL_NR",
        TF2HC0.TC0TD0_ZUST_C          AS "TC0TD0_ZUST_C",
        TF2HC0.TC0TD0_LF_NR           AS "TC0TD0_LF_NR",
        TF2HC0.TC0T18_ID_NR           AS "TF2HC0.TC0T18_ID_NR",
        TF2HC0.TC0TC0_LF_NR           AS "TF2HC0.TC0TC0_LF_NR",
        TF2TC2.TC0T18_ID_NR_2         AS "TC0T18_ID_NR_2",
        TF2TC2.TC0TC0_LF_NR_2         AS "TC0TC0_LF_NR_2",
        "2aLV2STLST".TC0TC0_LF_NR     AS "2aLV2STLST.TC0TC0_LF_NR",
        "2aLV2STLST".TC0T18_ID_NR     AS "2aLV2STLST.TC0T18_ID_NR"
    FROM
        (SELECT
        "1aLV1STLSTVertrag"."TF2HD0.GLT_AB" AS "TF2HD0.GLT_AB",
        "1aLV1STLSTVertrag"."GLT_BIS"       AS "TF2HD0.GLT_BIS",
        "1aLV1STLSTVertrag"."TF2HD0.ERF_AM" AS "TF2HD0.ERF_AM",
        

        TF2HC0.GLT_AB                       AS "TF2HC0.GLT_AB",
        TF2HC0.GLT_BIS                      AS "GLT_BIS",
        TF2HC0.ERF_AM                       AS "TF2HC0.ERF_AM",
        TF2HC0.ERS_AM                       AS "ERS_AM",
        TF2HC0.STAT_C                       AS "STAT_C",
        TF2HC0.GSFTV_STAT_C                 AS "GSFTV_STAT_C",
        TF2HC0.BEN_ID                       AS "BEN_ID",
        TF2HC0.TC0TD0_POL_NR                AS "TC0TD0_POL_NR",
        TF2HC0.TC0TD0_ZUST_C                AS "TC0TD0_ZUST_C",
        TF2HC0.TC0TD0_LF_NR                 AS "TC0TD0_LF_NR",
        TF2HC0.TC0T18_ID_NR                 AS "TC0T18_ID_NR",
        TF2HC0.TC0TC0_LF_NR                 AS "TC0TC0_LF_NR",
        TF2HC0.T31T31_ID_NR                 AS "T31T31_ID_NR"
    FROM 
        ( SELECT 
    
         TF2HD0.GLT_AB        AS "TF2HD0.GLT_AB"
        ,TF2HD0.GLT_BIS       AS "GLT_BIS"
        ,TF2HD0.ERF_AM        AS "TF2HD0.ERF_AM"
        ,TF2HD0.ERS_AM        AS "ERS_AM"
        ,TF2HD0.STAT_C        AS "STAT_C"
        ,TF2HD0.GSFTV_STAT_C  AS "GSFTV_STAT_C"
        ,TF2HD0.BEN_ID        AS "BEN_ID"
        ,TF2HD0.TD0TD0_LF_NR  AS "TD0TD0_LF_NR"
        ,TF2HD0.TD0TD0_ZUST_C AS "TD0TD0_ZUST_C"
        ,TF2HD0.TD0TD0_POL_NR AS "TD0TD0_POL_NR"
        ,TF2HD0.T31T31_ID_NR  AS "T31T31_ID_NR"
        ,TF2HD0.BEN_ID_BARB   AS "BEN_ID_BARB"
        ,TF2HD0.H18_ERF_AM    AS "H18_ERF_AM"
        ,TF4TEC.GLT_AB        AS "TF4TEC.GLT_AB"
        ,TF4TEC.ERF_AM        AS "TF4TEC.ERF_AM"
        ,TF4TEC.T18T18_ID_NR  AS "T18T18_ID_NR"
        ,TF4TEC.TD0_LF_NR     AS "TD0_LF_NR"
    FROM 
        CHZIS1_P2000.P2000.TF4TEC AS TF4TEC  
    INNER JOIN 
        CHZIS1_P2000.P2000.TF2HD0 AS TF2HD0 
        ON 
            (TF4TEC.GLT_AB = TF2HD0.GLT_AB) 
            AND (TF4TEC.ERF_AM = TF2HD0.ERF_AM) 
            AND (TF4TEC.TD0_LF_NR = TF2HD0.TD0TD0_LF_NR) 
            AND (TF4TEC.TD0_ZUST_C = TF2HD0.TD0TD0_ZUST_C) 
            AND (TF4TEC.TD0_POL_NR = TF2HD0.TD0TD0_POL_NR)
    WHERE 
        TF4TEC.TD0_POL_NR = 15780800 ) AS "1aLV1STLSTVertrag"
    INNER JOIN
        CHZIS1_P2000.P2000.TF2HC0 AS TF2HC0  
        ON 
            TF2HC0.TC0TD0_POL_NR     = "1aLV1STLSTVertrag".TD0TD0_POL_NR 
            AND TF2HC0.TC0TD0_ZUST_C = "1aLV1STLSTVertrag".TD0TD0_ZUST_C 
            AND TF2HC0.TC0TD0_LF_NR  = "1aLV1STLSTVertrag".TD0TD0_LF_NR
            AND TF2HC0.GLT_AB       <= "1aLV1STLSTVertrag"."TF2HD0.GLT_AB"
            AND TF2HC0.GLT_BIS      >= "1aLV1STLSTVertrag"."TF2HD0.GLT_AB" 
            AND TF2HC0.ERF_AM       <= "1aLV1STLSTVertrag"."TF2HD0.ERF_AM"
            AND TF2HC0.ERS_AM        > "1aLV1STLSTVertrag"."TF2HD0.ERF_AM"

            
            AND TF2HC0.STAT_C        = "1aLV1STLSTVertrag".STAT_C

    WHERE
        TF2HC0.TC0T18_ID_NR IN (10682)) AS "2aLV2STLST"
    INNER JOIN 
        CHZIS1_P2000.P2000.TF2TC2 AS TF2TC2   
        ON
                "2aLV2STLST".TC0TD0_POL_NR = TF2TC2.TC0TD0_POL_NR_2
            AND "2aLV2STLST".TC0TD0_ZUST_C = TF2TC2.TC0TD0_ZUST_C_2
            AND "2aLV2STLST".TC0TD0_LF_NR  = TF2TC2.TC0TD0_LF_NR_2
            AND "2aLV2STLST".TC0T18_ID_NR  = TF2TC2.TC0T18_ID_NR_2
            AND "2aLV2STLST".TC0TC0_LF_NR  = TF2TC2.TC0TC0_LF_NR_2

    INNER JOIN 
        CHZIS1_P2000.P2000.TF2HC0 AS TF2HC0 
        ON 
                TF2TC2.TC0TD0_POL_NR_1 = TF2HC0.TC0TD0_POL_NR
            AND TF2TC2.TC0TD0_ZUST_C_1 = TF2HC0.TC0TD0_ZUST_C
            AND TF2TC2.TC0TD0_LF_NR_1  = TF2HC0.TC0TD0_LF_NR
            AND TF2TC2.TC0T18_ID_NR_1  = TF2HC0.TC0T18_ID_NR
            AND TF2TC2.TC0TC0_LF_NR_1  = TF2HC0.TC0TC0_LF_NR

    WHERE 
            TF2HC0.GLT_AB  <= "2aLV2STLST"."TF2HD0.GLT_AB"
        AND TF2HC0.GLT_BIS >= "2aLV2STLST"."TF2HD0.GLT_AB"
        AND TF2HC0.ERF_AM  <= "2aLV2STLST"."TF2HD0.ERF_AM"
        AND TF2HC0.ERS_AM  >  "2aLV2STLST"."TF2HD0.ERF_AM" ) AS "3aLv3STLST" 

    INNER JOIN 
        CHZIS1_P2000.P2000.TF2TG0 AS TF2TG0  
            ON      "3aLv3STLST"."TF2HC0.TC0TC0_LF_NR" = TF2TG0.TC0TC0_LF_NR
                AND "3aLv3STLST"."TF2HC0.TC0T18_ID_NR" = TF2TG0.TC0T18_ID_NR
                AND "3aLv3STLST".TC0TD0_LF_NR          = TF2TG0.TC0TD0_LF_NR
                AND "3aLv3STLST".TC0TD0_ZUST_C         = TF2TG0.TC0TD0_ZUST_C
                AND "3aLv3STLST".TC0TD0_POL_NR         = TF2TG0.TC0TD0_POL_NR

    INNER JOIN 
        CHZIS1_P2000.P2000.TF2HG0 AS TF2HG0  
            ON 
                TF2TG0.ID_NR = TF2HG0.TG0TG0_ID_NR
    INNER JOIN 
        CHZIS1_P2000.P2000.TF2TG1 AS TF2TG1   
        ON 
            TF2HG0.TG0TG0_ID_NR = TF2TG1.TG0TG0_ID_NR
    WHERE 
            TF2HG0.GLT_AB  <= "3aLv3STLST".GLT_AB 
        AND TF2HG0.GLT_BIS >= "3aLv3STLST".GLT_AB 
        AND TF2HG0.ERF_AM  <= "3aLv3STLST".ERF_AM 
        AND TF2HG0.ERS_AM  >  "3aLv3STLST".ERF_AM 
        AND TF2TG1.GLT_AB  <= "3aLv3STLST".GLT_AB 
        AND TF2TG1.GLT_BIS >= "3aLv3STLST".GLT_AB 
        AND TF2TG1.ERF_AM  <= "3aLv3STLST".ERF_AM 
        AND TF2TG1.ERS_AM  >  "3aLv3STLST".ERF_AM
Hash256(STLST_TD0TD0_POL_NR, STLST_TD0TD0_ZUST_C, STLST_TD0TD0_LF_NR, STLST_T18T18_ID_NR, STLST_LF_NR) AS [%STLST_Objekte]

SELECT
        "1aLV1STLSTVertrag".T18T18_ID_NR    AS "T18T18_ID_NR",              
        "1aLV1STLSTVertrag".TD0_LF_NR       AS "TD0_LF_NR",                 

        "1aLV1STLSTVertrag"."TF2HD0.GLT_AB" AS "TF2HD0.GLT_AB",             
        "1aLV1STLSTVertrag".GLT_BIS         AS "1aLV1STLSTVertrag.GLT_BIS",
        "1aLV1STLSTVertrag"."TF2HD0.ERF_AM" AS "TF2HD0.ERF_AM",             

    
        TF2TG0.ID_NR                        AS "ID_NR",                     
        TF2TG0.KL_C                         AS "KL_C",
        TF2TG0.ABH_ROL_C                    AS "ABH_ROL_C",
        TF2TG0.DMY                          AS "DMY",
        TF2TG0.FKT_C                        AS "FKT_C",
        TF2TG0.FKT_NR                       AS "FKT_NR",
        TF2TG0.T20T20_ID_NR                 AS "T20T20_ID_NR",
        TF2TG0.TC0TD0_POL_NR                AS "TC0TD0_POL_NR",
        TF2TG0.TC0TD0_ZUST_C                AS "TC0TD0_ZUST_C",
        TF2TG0.TC0TD0_LF_NR                 AS "TC0TD0_LF_NR",
        TF2TG0.TC0T18_ID_NR                 AS "TC0T18_ID_NR",
        TF2TG0.TC0TC0_LF_NR                 AS "TC0TC0_LF_NR",
        TF2TG0.TD0TD0_LF_NR                 AS "TD0TD0_LF_NR",
        TF2TG0.TD0TD0_ZUST_C                AS "TD0TD0_ZUST_C",
        TF2TG0.TD0TD0_POL_NR                AS "TD0TD0_POL_NR",
        TF2TG0.TZ0TZ0_ID_NR                 AS "TZ0TZ0_ID_NR",
        TF2TG0.LF_NR                        AS "LF_NR",
        TF2TG0.TZ0_ID_NR                    AS "TZ0_ID_NR",

    
        TF2HG0.GLT_AB                       AS "TF2HG0.GLT_AB",
        TF2HG0.GLT_BIS                      AS "TF2HG0.GLT_BIS",
        TF2HG0.ERF_AM                       AS "TF2HG0.ERF_AM",
        TF2HG0.ERS_AM                       AS "1bV1KLS.ERS_AM",
        TF2HG0.LOE_C                        AS "1bV1KLS.LOE_C",
        TF2HG0.TG0TG0_ID_NR                 AS "TG0TG0_ID_NR",

    
        TF2TG1.GLT_AB                       AS "TF2TG1.GLT_AB",
        TF2TG1.GLT_BIS                      AS "TF2TG1.GLT_BIS",
        TF2TG1.ERF_AM                       AS "TF2TG1.ERF_AM",
        TF2TG1.ERS_AM                       AS "TF2TG1.ERS_AM",
        TF2TG1.UNIV_WERT                    AS "UNIV_WERT",
        TF2TG1.LOE_C                        AS "TF2TG1.LOE_C",
        TF2TG1.TG0TG0_ID_NR                 AS "TF2TG1.TG0TG0_ID_NR",
        TF2TG1.T19T19_ID_NR                 AS "T19T19_ID_NR"

    FROM 
        ( SELECT 
    
         TF2HD0.GLT_AB        AS "TF2HD0.GLT_AB"
        ,TF2HD0.GLT_BIS       AS "GLT_BIS"
        ,TF2HD0.ERF_AM        AS "TF2HD0.ERF_AM"
        ,TF2HD0.ERS_AM        AS "ERS_AM"
        ,TF2HD0.STAT_C        AS "STAT_C"
        ,TF2HD0.GSFTV_STAT_C  AS "GSFTV_STAT_C"
        ,TF2HD0.BEN_ID        AS "BEN_ID"
        ,TF2HD0.TD0TD0_LF_NR  AS "TD0TD0_LF_NR"
        ,TF2HD0.TD0TD0_ZUST_C AS "TD0TD0_ZUST_C"
        ,TF2HD0.TD0TD0_POL_NR AS "TD0TD0_POL_NR"
        ,TF2HD0.T31T31_ID_NR  AS "T31T31_ID_NR"
        ,TF2HD0.BEN_ID_BARB   AS "BEN_ID_BARB"
        ,TF2HD0.H18_ERF_AM    AS "H18_ERF_AM"
        ,TF4TEC.GLT_AB        AS "TF4TEC.GLT_AB"
        ,TF4TEC.ERF_AM        AS "TF4TEC.ERF_AM"
        ,TF4TEC.T18T18_ID_NR  AS "T18T18_ID_NR"
        ,TF4TEC.TD0_LF_NR     AS "TD0_LF_NR"
    FROM 
        CHZIS1_P2000.P2000.TF4TEC AS TF4TEC  
    INNER JOIN 
        CHZIS1_P2000.P2000.TF2HD0 AS TF2HD0 
        ON 
            (TF4TEC.GLT_AB = TF2HD0.GLT_AB) 
            AND (TF4TEC.ERF_AM = TF2HD0.ERF_AM) 
            AND (TF4TEC.TD0_LF_NR = TF2HD0.TD0TD0_LF_NR) 
            AND (TF4TEC.TD0_ZUST_C = TF2HD0.TD0TD0_ZUST_C) 
            AND (TF4TEC.TD0_POL_NR = TF2HD0.TD0TD0_POL_NR)
    WHERE 
        TF4TEC.TD0_POL_NR = 15780800 ) AS "1aLV1STLSTVertrag"
    INNER JOIN
        CHZIS1_P2000.P2000.TF2TG0 AS TF2TG0   
        ON 
            "1aLV1STLSTVertrag".TD0TD0_POL_NR     =  TF2TG0.TD0TD0_POL_NR 
            AND "1aLV1STLSTVertrag".TD0TD0_LF_NR  =  TF2TG0.TD0TD0_LF_NR 
            AND "1aLV1STLSTVertrag".TD0TD0_ZUST_C =  TF2TG0.TD0TD0_ZUST_C     
    INNER JOIN 
        CHZIS1_P2000.P2000.TF2HG0 AS TF2HG0   
        ON
            TF2TG0.ID_NR                     =  TF2HG0.TG0TG0_ID_NR
            AND TF2HG0.GLT_AB                <= "1aLV1STLSTVertrag"."TF2HD0.GLT_AB" 
            AND TF2HG0.ERF_AM                <= "1aLV1STLSTVertrag"."TF2HD0.ERF_AM" 
            AND TF2HG0.ERS_AM                >  "1aLV1STLSTVertrag"."TF2HD0.ERF_AM" 
            AND TF2HG0.GLT_BIS               >= "1aLV1STLSTVertrag"."TF2HD0.GLT_AB"

    INNER JOIN
        CHZIS1_P2000.P2000.TF2TG1 AS TF2TG1    
        ON
            
            TF2TG0.ID_NR         = TF2TG1.TG0TG0_ID_NR
            
            AND TF2TG1."GLT_AB" <= "1aLV1STLSTVertrag"."TF2HD0.GLT_AB" 
            
            AND TF2TG1.GLT_BIS  >= "1aLV1STLSTVertrag"."TF2HD0.GLT_AB"
            
            AND TF2TG1.ERF_AM   <= "1aLV1STLSTVertrag"."TF2HD0.ERF_AM"
            
            AND TF2TG1.ERS_AM   > "1aLV1STLSTVertrag"."TF2HD0.ERF_AM"

SELECT 
    
         TF2HD0.GLT_AB        AS "TF2HD0.GLT_AB"
        ,TF2HD0.GLT_BIS       AS "GLT_BIS"
        ,TF2HD0.ERF_AM        AS "TF2HD0.ERF_AM"
        ,TF2HD0.ERS_AM        AS "ERS_AM"
        ,TF2HD0.STAT_C        AS "STAT_C"
        ,TF2HD0.GSFTV_STAT_C  AS "GSFTV_STAT_C"
        ,TF2HD0.BEN_ID        AS "BEN_ID"
        ,TF2HD0.TD0TD0_LF_NR  AS "TD0TD0_LF_NR"
        ,TF2HD0.TD0TD0_ZUST_C AS "TD0TD0_ZUST_C"
        ,TF2HD0.TD0TD0_POL_NR AS "TD0TD0_POL_NR"
        ,TF2HD0.T31T31_ID_NR  AS "T31T31_ID_NR"
        ,TF2HD0.BEN_ID_BARB   AS "BEN_ID_BARB"
        ,TF2HD0.H18_ERF_AM    AS "H18_ERF_AM"
        ,TF4TEC.GLT_AB        AS "TF4TEC.GLT_AB"
        ,TF4TEC.ERF_AM        AS "TF4TEC.ERF_AM"
        ,TF4TEC.T18T18_ID_NR  AS "T18T18_ID_NR"
        ,TF4TEC.TD0_LF_NR     AS "TD0_LF_NR"
    FROM 
        CHZIS1_P2000.P2000.TF4TEC AS TF4TEC  
    INNER JOIN 
        CHZIS1_P2000.P2000.TF2HD0 AS TF2HD0 
        ON 
            (TF4TEC.GLT_AB = TF2HD0.GLT_AB) 
            AND (TF4TEC.ERF_AM = TF2HD0.ERF_AM) 
            AND (TF4TEC.TD0_LF_NR = TF2HD0.TD0TD0_LF_NR) 
            AND (TF4TEC.TD0_ZUST_C = TF2HD0.TD0TD0_ZUST_C) 
            AND (TF4TEC.TD0_POL_NR = TF2HD0.TD0TD0_POL_NR)
    WHERE 
        TF4TEC.TD0_POL_NR = 15780800
Hash256(Obj_Vertrag_NR, Obj_Vertrag_ZUST_C, Obj_Vertrag_LF_NR, Obj_T18_ID_NR, Obj_TC0TC0_LF_NR) AS [%STLST_Objekte]
Hash256(T18_ID_NR, T20_ID_NR, T30_R, T19_ID_NR) AS [%Attribute_KTG Mapping]

SELECT
        "2aLV2STLST"."TF2HD0.GLT_AB"  AS "GLT_AB",
        "2aLV2STLST"."TF2HD0.GLT_BIS" AS "GLT_BIS",
        "2aLV2STLST"."TF2HD0.ERF_AM"  AS "ERF_AM",
        TF2HC0.TC0TD0_POL_NR          AS "TC0TD0_POL_NR",
        TF2HC0.TC0TD0_ZUST_C          AS "TC0TD0_ZUST_C",
        TF2HC0.TC0TD0_LF_NR           AS "TC0TD0_LF_NR",
        TF2HC0.TC0T18_ID_NR           AS "TF2HC0.TC0T18_ID_NR",
        TF2HC0.TC0TC0_LF_NR           AS "TF2HC0.TC0TC0_LF_NR",
        TF2TC2.TC0T18_ID_NR_2         AS "TC0T18_ID_NR_2",
        TF2TC2.TC0TC0_LF_NR_2         AS "TC0TC0_LF_NR_2",
        "2aLV2STLST".TC0TC0_LF_NR     AS "2aLV2STLST.TC0TC0_LF_NR",
        "2aLV2STLST".TC0T18_ID_NR     AS "2aLV2STLST.TC0T18_ID_NR"
    FROM
        (SELECT
        "1aLV1STLSTVertrag"."TF2HD0.GLT_AB" AS "TF2HD0.GLT_AB",
        "1aLV1STLSTVertrag"."GLT_BIS"       AS "TF2HD0.GLT_BIS",
        "1aLV1STLSTVertrag"."TF2HD0.ERF_AM" AS "TF2HD0.ERF_AM",
        

        TF2HC0.GLT_AB                       AS "TF2HC0.GLT_AB",
        TF2HC0.GLT_BIS                      AS "GLT_BIS",
        TF2HC0.ERF_AM                       AS "TF2HC0.ERF_AM",
        TF2HC0.ERS_AM                       AS "ERS_AM",
        TF2HC0.STAT_C                       AS "STAT_C",
        TF2HC0.GSFTV_STAT_C                 AS "GSFTV_STAT_C",
        TF2HC0.BEN_ID                       AS "BEN_ID",
        TF2HC0.TC0TD0_POL_NR                AS "TC0TD0_POL_NR",
        TF2HC0.TC0TD0_ZUST_C                AS "TC0TD0_ZUST_C",
        TF2HC0.TC0TD0_LF_NR                 AS "TC0TD0_LF_NR",
        TF2HC0.TC0T18_ID_NR                 AS "TC0T18_ID_NR",
        TF2HC0.TC0TC0_LF_NR                 AS "TC0TC0_LF_NR",
        TF2HC0.T31T31_ID_NR                 AS "T31T31_ID_NR"
    FROM 
        ( SELECT 
    
         TF2HD0.GLT_AB        AS "TF2HD0.GLT_AB"
        ,TF2HD0.GLT_BIS       AS "GLT_BIS"
        ,TF2HD0.ERF_AM        AS "TF2HD0.ERF_AM"
        ,TF2HD0.ERS_AM        AS "ERS_AM"
        ,TF2HD0.STAT_C        AS "STAT_C"
        ,TF2HD0.GSFTV_STAT_C  AS "GSFTV_STAT_C"
        ,TF2HD0.BEN_ID        AS "BEN_ID"
        ,TF2HD0.TD0TD0_LF_NR  AS "TD0TD0_LF_NR"
        ,TF2HD0.TD0TD0_ZUST_C AS "TD0TD0_ZUST_C"
        ,TF2HD0.TD0TD0_POL_NR AS "TD0TD0_POL_NR"
        ,TF2HD0.T31T31_ID_NR  AS "T31T31_ID_NR"
        ,TF2HD0.BEN_ID_BARB   AS "BEN_ID_BARB"
        ,TF2HD0.H18_ERF_AM    AS "H18_ERF_AM"
        ,TF4TEC.GLT_AB        AS "TF4TEC.GLT_AB"
        ,TF4TEC.ERF_AM        AS "TF4TEC.ERF_AM"
        ,TF4TEC.T18T18_ID_NR  AS "T18T18_ID_NR"
        ,TF4TEC.TD0_LF_NR     AS "TD0_LF_NR"
    FROM 
        CHZIS1_P2000.P2000.TF4TEC AS TF4TEC  
    INNER JOIN 
        CHZIS1_P2000.P2000.TF2HD0 AS TF2HD0 
        ON 
            (TF4TEC.GLT_AB = TF2HD0.GLT_AB) 
            AND (TF4TEC.ERF_AM = TF2HD0.ERF_AM) 
            AND (TF4TEC.TD0_LF_NR = TF2HD0.TD0TD0_LF_NR)
